  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A meeting between the Chinese ambassador and the foreign minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting has been held between the Minister of Foreign Affairs Mr. Ali Sabri and the Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Mr. Chi Shenhong. The meeting was held at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs.",
        "At the beginning, Ambassador Shenhong congratulated the Foreign Minister on his new appointment and also handed over the congratulatory message of the State Councilor and Foreign Minister of China Mr. Wang.",
        "The Minister of Foreign Affairs stated that Sri Lanka and China are traditional friends with long-term bilateral and economic relations. Both sides expressed great satisfaction over the strong bilateral relations, including the existing relations between governments and people-to-people.",
        "Senior officials of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and officials of the Chinese Embassy also participated in the meeting."
      ],
